&lt;p&gt;If some special handling had been required to avoid/fix the bug, I agree big comment would be in place.&lt;/p&gt;</comment>
                            <comment id="12479830" author="sv204098" created="Sat, 10 Mar 2007 12:05:18 +0000"  >&lt;p&gt;Thanks Krisitan for looking at the patch &amp;amp; your valuable comments.&lt;br/&gt;
